{"id":264,"date":"2025-01-23T23:40:58","date_gmt":"2025-01-23T23:40:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/donation.nicdark.com\/charity-wordpress-theme\/?post_type=product&#038;p=264"},"modified":"2025-02-25T08:54:28","modified_gmt":"2025-02-25T08:54:28","slug":"product-1","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/donation.nicdark.com\/homeless-wordpress-theme\/product\/product-1\/","title":{"rendered":"Blanket Kit"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"product-post\" data-elementor-id=\"264\" class=\"elementor elementor-264\" data-elementor-post-type=\"product\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d84312 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2d84312\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-883ab2c e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"883ab2c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7983ddb elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7983ddb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Our mission is to deliver critical resources to refugees displaced by war and conflict. These essential kits are designed to provide immediate support to those who need it most. Whether it's the warmth of a blanket during a cold night, the safety of clean water, or the care provided through medical supplies.<\/p>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee11123 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ee11123\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a351326 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a351326\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0bad648 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"0bad648\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Essential Aid<\/h5>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9d551c6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"9d551c6\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-663c83e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"663c83e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Emergency Relief<\/h5>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-75da551 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"75da551\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-26eed66 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"26eed66\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Each product is carefully selected to make a tangible difference in the lives of vulnerable individuals. With your help, we can ensure that these life-saving items reach refugees in need, offering them the protection, comfort, and hope they deserve. Your contribution plays a crucial role in helping rebuild lives.<\/p>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f5fcb74 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f5fcb74\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f9a86e5 elementor-blockquote--skin-boxed elementor-blockquote--align-left elementor-blockquote--button-color-custom elementor-blockquote--button-view-icon-text elementor-blockquote--button-skin-classic elementor-widget elementor-widget-blockquote\" data-id=\"f9a86e5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"blockquote.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote class=\"elementor-blockquote\">\n\t\t\t<p class=\"elementor-blockquote__content\">\n\t\t\t\tIn the face of crisis, the kindness and compassion we extend to others can create a ripple of change. Every small act of giving, every kit provided, and every life touched, brings us one step closer to a better world.\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-q-footer\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite class=\"elementor-blockquote__author\">Michael Davis<\/cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/intent\/tweet?text=In+the+face+of+crisis%2C+the+kindness+and+compassion+we+extend+to+others+can+create+a+ripple+of+change.+Every+small+act+of+giving%2C+every+kit+provided%2C+and+every+life+touched%2C+brings+us+one+step+closer+to+a+better+world.+%E2%80%94+Michael+Davis&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fdonation.nicdark.com%2Fhomeless-wordpress-theme%2Fhomeless-wordpress-theme%2Fproduct%2Fproduct-1%2F\" class=\"elementor-blockquote__tweet-button\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fab-twitter\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M459.37 151.716c.325 4.548.325 9.097.325 13.645 0 138.72-105.583 298.558-298.558 298.558-59.452 0-114.68-17.219-161.137-47.106 8.447.974 16.568 1.299 25.34 1.299 49.055 0 94.213-16.568 130.274-44.832-46.132-.975-84.792-31.188-98.112-72.772 6.498.974 12.995 1.624 19.818 1.624 9.421 0 18.843-1.3 27.614-3.573-48.081-9.747-84.143-51.98-84.143-102.985v-1.299c13.969 7.797 30.214 12.67 47.431 13.319-28.264-18.843-4